---
---

<section id="offerings" class="sprints-section">
	<div class="container">
		<div class="sprints-header reveal">
			<p class="badge">HOW WE WORK</p>
			<h2 class="serif-h2">Four ways to work together.</h2>
			<p class="subhead-sprints">
				The company with the clearest story wins the deals, the hires, and the next round. Yours should.
			</p>
		</div>
		
		<!-- Reverting to bento-grid class for staggered animation compatibility -->
		<div class="bento-grid grid-four">
			<!-- Founder Storytelling -->
			<div class="bento-card anodized sheen">
				<div class="card-inner-v2">
					<div class="sprint-header">
						<p class="tagline">2–4 WEEKS</p>
						<h3 class="serif-h3">Founder Storytelling</h3>
					</div>
					<p class="hook">
						You know what you're building. Getting the market to believe it is a different problem. We find the version of your story that's impossible to copy, then put it in the rooms that change outcomes.
					</p>
					<div class="outputs-list">
						<p class="output-label">OUTPUTS</p>
						<ul>
							<li>Founder story ready for investors, press, recruiting, and customers.</li>
							<li>Channel strategy built around where your buyers actually pay attention.</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					<a href="#contact" class="btn-sprint-minimal">Start Story</a>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Positioning Sprint -->
			<div class="bento-card anodized sheen">
				<div class="card-inner-v2">
					<div class="sprint-header">
						<p class="tagline">2–5 WEEKS</p>
						<h3 class="serif-h3">Positioning Sprint</h3>
					</div>
					<p class="hook">
						You're losing deals you should be winning. Usually it's not the product. We interview your customers and your losses, then build positioning from the evidence up.
					</p>
					<div class="outputs-list">
						<p class="output-label">OUTPUTS</p>
						<ul>
							<li>Positioning deck built from customer interviews and win/loss data.</li>
							<li>First call deck that closes the gap between interest and next meeting.</li>
							<li>Homepage blueprint that converts the right visitors.</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					<a href="#contact" class="btn-sprint-minimal">Start Positioning</a>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- The Growth Protocol -->
			<div class="bento-card anodized sheen">
				<div class="card-inner-v2">
					<div class="sprint-header">
						<p class="tagline">6–8 WEEKS</p>
						<h3 class="serif-h3">The Growth Protocol</h3>
					</div>
					<p class="hook">
						Growth is slower than the board expects and you know something is blocking it. We find it, name it, and build the 90-day plan around the moves that will actually change the number.
					</p>
					<div class="outputs-list">
						<p class="output-label">OUTPUTS</p>
						<ul>
							<li>Diagnostic memo showing exactly where deals stall and why.</li>
							<li>90-day roadmap with three to five prioritized moves.</li>
							<li>Your next hire identified by the bottleneck it solves.</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					<a href="#contact" class="btn-sprint-minimal">Start Protocol</a>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Marketing Systems -->
			<div class="bento-card anodized sheen">
				<div class="card-inner-v2">
					<div class="sprint-header">
						<p class="tagline">2–4 MONTHS</p>
						<h3 class="serif-h3">Marketing Systems</h3>
					</div>
					<p class="hook">
						Your team spends most of their time on execution and not enough on the work that moves the number. We build the systems that change that ratio.
					</p>
					<div class="outputs-list">
						<p class="output-label">OUTPUTS</p>
						<ul>
							<li>Custom workflows built around your team's actual workload.</li>
							<li>A clear framework for where systems run and where your team leads.</li>
							<li>Onboarding that drives real adoption, not shelf life.</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					<a href="#contact" class="btn-sprint-minimal">Start Systems</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.sprints-section { padding: 5rem 0; position: relative; }

	.sprints-header {
		text-align: left;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		gap: 2rem;
		align-items: end;
	}

	.serif-h2 {
		font-family: var(--font-serif);
		font-size: 3rem;
		margin-bottom: 0;
		line-height: 1.1;
		font-weight: 400;
	}

	.subhead-sprints {
		font-family: var(--font-sans);
		font-size: 1rem;
		color: var(--fg-muted);
		max-width: 400px;
		line-height: 1.6;
		font-style: normal;
		letter-spacing: 0.02rem;
	}

	.bento-grid.grid-four {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
		gap: 1px;
		z-index: 2;
		position: relative;
		border: 1px solid var(--border-dim);
	}

	.bento-card {
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
		border-right: 1px solid var(--border-dim);
		border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-dim);
		position: relative;
		overflow: hidden;
		transition: background 0.3s ease;
		display: flex;
		opacity: 0;
		transform: translateY(20px);
	}

	:global(.bento-card.active) { opacity: 1 !important; transform: translateY(0) !important; }

	.card-inner-v2 {
		padding: 2.5rem;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		width: 100%;
	}

	.anodized:hover {
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
	}

	.tagline {
		font-size: 0.6rem;
		letter-spacing: 0.2rem;
		color: var(--p-orange);
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		font-weight: 900;
	}

	.serif-h3 {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
		line-height: 1.2;
		font-family: var(--font-serif);
		min-height: 3.6rem;
		font-weight: 400;
	}

	.hook {
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		color: var(--fg-muted);
		line-height: 1.5;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.outputs-list {
		flex-grow: 1;
		margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
	}

	.output-label {
		font-size: 0.55rem;
		font-weight: 900;
		letter-spacing: 0.15rem;
		color: var(--p-sky);
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(180, 184, 240, 0.2);
		padding-bottom: 0.4rem;
		display: inline-block;
	}

	.outputs-list ul {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
		margin: 0;
	}

	.outputs-list li {
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		color: var(--fg-white);
		line-height: 1.4;
		margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
		position: relative;
		padding-left: 1rem;
	}

	.outputs-list li::before {
		content: "—";
		position: absolute;
		left: 0;
		color: var(--p-orange);
		opacity: 0.6;
	}

	.btn-sprint-minimal {
		text-decoration: none;
		color: var(--fg-white);
		font-size: 0.72rem;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.12rem;
		padding-bottom: 0.25rem;
		border-bottom: 1px solid var(--p-orange);
		display: inline-block;
		transition: color 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
		margin-top: auto;
	}

	.btn-sprint-minimal:hover {
		color: var(--p-orange);
	}

	@media (max-width: 1200px) {
		.bento-grid.grid-four { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
		.serif-h2 { font-size: 2.8rem; }
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.sprints-section { padding: 4rem 0; }
		.bento-grid.grid-four { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
		.serif-h2 { font-size: 2.2rem; }
		.subhead-sprints { font-size: 1.15rem; }
		.bento-card { min-height: auto; transform: none !important; }
	}
</style>